ra.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_004-270x209.jpg 270w" sizes="(max-width: 257px) 100vw, 257px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="120" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_03-120x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="THau_03" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_03-120x200.jpg 120w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_03-462x768.jpg 462w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_03-270x448.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_03.jpg 1156w" sizes="(max-width: 120px) 100vw, 120px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="121" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_003-121x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="THau_003" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_003-121x200.jpg 121w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_003-467x768.jpg 467w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_003-270x443.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_003.jpg 1169w" sizes="(max-width: 121px) 100vw, 121px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="125" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_02-125x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="THau_02" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_02-125x200.jpg 125w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_02-480x768.jpg 480w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_02-270x431.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_02.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 125px) 100vw, 125px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="121" height="200" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_002-121x200.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="THau_002" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/THau_002-121x200.jpg 121w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-cont